T02D1894:233a-1: shr'i guhya sa m'a dza sto tra /
T02D1894:233a-3: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i bstod pa /
T02D1894:233a-4: 'jam pa'i rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233a-5: kun du rtog pa ma lus spangs //
T02D1894:233a-6: dri ma dang bral bdag nyid can //
T02D1894:233a-7: kun bzang chos dbyings ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233a-8: mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233a-9: ston ka'i zla ba ltar dkar ba //
T02D1894:233a-11: me long ye shes ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233a-12: rnam snang gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233a-13: lta ngan rtog pa dang bral zhing //
T02D1894:233a-14: skyon med mkha' ltar rnam par dag / mnyam nyid ye shes ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233a-15: rin chen dbang la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233a-16: dpag med 'od kyi mkha' kun khyab //
T02D1894:233a-17: tshad med yon tan phreng ba yis //
T02D1894:233a-18: kun rtog ye shes mkhyen pa yi //
T02D1894:233a-20: 'gro ba'i don ni mdzad pa po //
T02D1894:233a-22: bya grub ye shes ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233a-23: don yod grub pa de la 'dud //
T02D1894:233a-24: sa ltar sems can thams cad kyi /
T02D1894:233a-25: mchog tu rnam par 'dzin spyod pa //
T02D1894:233a-26: thugs rje spyod pa g-yo ba po //
T02D1894:233a-27: lha mo spyan mar phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233a-28: gang gi mthu yis sems can rnams //
T02D1894:233a-29: nyan mongs nyid ni rab zhi ba //
T02D1894:233a-30: chu ltar phan pa don chen gyi //
T02D1894:233b-0: m'a ma k'i la phyag 'tshal @233b lo ;
T02D1894:233b-1: / me ltar sems can thams cad kyi //
T02D1894:233b-2: nyon mongs nyid ni bsreg par brtson //
T02D1894:233b-3: bya ba rtse mo mchog grub pa //
T02D1894:233b-4: na bza' dkar mor phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-5: rlung ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa'i //
T02D1894:233b-8: sgrol ma la ni phyag 'tshal lo ;
T02D1894:233b-9: / gang gi gzugs ni rgya che zhing //
T02D1894:233b-10: rnam pa kun du mi 'phro ba //
T02D1894:233b-11: brtags bral gzugs kyi rdo rje ma //
T02D1894:233b-12: mnyam med de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-13: gang gi mthu yis sgra rnams kyi //
T02D1894:233b-14: de nyid dam pa gsung rgyas shing //
T02D1894:233b-15: rna ba'i bde ba stsol mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-16: sgra rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-17: gang gi longs spyod lhun grub pa //
T02D1894:233b-18: sems can ma lus la sems pa'i //
T02D1894:233b-19: bung ba'i sgra mdzad rdo rje dri //
T02D1894:233b-20: ma smad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-21: gang gi rang rig brtan du med //
T02D1894:233b-22: gnyis med ro myang stobs kyis su //
T02D1894:233b-23: sems can bde la gnas mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-24: ro rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-26: re ba gang la sred mtha' ru //
T02D1894:233b-27: 'gro gsung rtag tu dga' mdzad pa'i //
T02D1894:233b-28: reg rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-29: gang phyir kun nas nyon mongs pa //
T02D1894:233b-30: gcod pa'i rgyud gyur chos rnams kyis //
T02D1894:233b-31: kun la rtag tu rtog mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-32: bla med chos kyi rdo rje 'dud ;
T02D1894:233b-33: / gang phyir theg pa chen po la //
T02D1894:233b-34: mi rnams dga' ba skyed mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-35: dad pa rnam dag ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233b-36: gshin rje gshed por phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-37: mkhas pa gang gis stobs kyis su //
T02D1894:233b-38: byang chub tshogs rnams rdzogs mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-39: brtson 'grus rnam dag ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233b-40: shes rab mthar byed phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1894:233b-41: gang gi mthu yis sems can rnams //
T02D1894:233b-42: dge ba brjed med skyed mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-43: dran pa rnam dag ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233b-45: gang gi stobs kyis sems can rnams //
T02D1894:233b-46: bgegs bral bde la gnas mdzad pa //
T02D1894:233b-47: bsam gtan rnam dag ngo bo nyid //
T02D1894:233b-49: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i bstod pa slob dpon chen
T02D1894:233b-50: po mar me mdzad ye shes kyis mdzad pa rdzogs
